---
title: Coconut, Lemongrass & Ginger Chicken with Asian Sesame Veggies & Garlic Rice
description: Asian cuisine comes together in a flash tonight. The secret? We’ve doubled up on superstar ingredients, with an aromatic
ginger-lemongrass coconut sauce and garlic rice so it smells and tastes like a tropical holiday.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/coconut-lemongrass-ginger-chicken-5ac041a9.jpg
